{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"09d8de11d3","title":"军委关于撤回新疆入藏部队问题致王震电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"175abf787d","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":25,"articleId":"09d8de11d3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e84f82ab3e","name":"王震","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"661310e2c3","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王震，当时任中共中央新疆分局书记、中国人民解放军新疆军区代司令员兼代政治委员。"},{"id":"c3c41fe670","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指王震1951年2月22日给军委、西北局、西北军区并请转西南军区的电报。电报说，新疆独立骑兵师入藏先道部队，已进驻藏北僧可日区之礼麻忙保。该区海拔在4000米以上，天气变化无常，时冷时热，空气稀薄，人马呼吸均感困难，病员逐渐增多。据先遗部队报告，该部135人，已病亡6人，现病34人，马匹病亡更加严重。我们除给入藏先遗部队以慰勉外，告其检查治疗，并令军区卫生部研究预防治疗方法，候开山后补送药品。"}],"contents":[{"id":"fa6db94f2b","type":"title","text":"军委关于撤回新疆人藏部队问题致王震电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3"},{"id":"661310e2c3","type":"paragraph","text":"王震，并告西北局，西北军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3"},{"id":"c3c41fe670","type":"paragraph","text":"丑养电悉。先造部队既如此困难，请考虑于开山后将该部队撤回新疆，尔后新疆即解除入藏任务，你是否同意这样做，盼告","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3"},{"id":"e17245817e","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3"},{"id":"12e3e68544","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3"}],"page":{"id":"57f22887d0","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"09d8de11d3","start":139,"end":139}}}},"__N_SSG":true}